description: This big ole blue truck is wagging its way through Central Texas and blazing up plates of the best doggone brisket, ribs, beef, (and more) that you’ll find in the Lone Star State. And you better believe that this rotisserie-style BBQ is finger lickin’ delicious. Their sides include coleslaw, potato salad, and luscious loaded fries. Local folks love this quality food so come out and bite (don’t bark) into some Big Dog BBQ. You’ll most likely share their positive point of view.
name: Big Dog BBQ
